==Using Google Chrome==

Unmask a required Google Chrome version:
{{rootCmd|<nowiki>echo '>=www-client/google-chrome-37.0.2062.120_p1' | tee -a package.accept_{keywords/netflix,keywords}</nowiki>}}

Emerge Google Chrome:
{{rootCmd|emerge -atv google-chrome}}

